Hi, I would just like to give a little warning about Gingko Biloba.



I am an 18 year old swedish student that for some time has taken Gingko pills. (pure EGb 761) Two per day. And when I for two days forgot to eat them I became Extreamly tired. (!)



I didn't manage to get out of bed at all for a day, hardly able to lift my arms, feeling tired for several days following. I meen I could get out of bed but in the same way I probably can run five miles at top speed to if I tried\ldots 



I am now taking them again and feeling fine but I thought you should know the story.  I don't think it's such a big deal and I don't know if this is a single case with just me but\ldots   knowledge is knowledge.
